DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T200000
SUMMARY:Pronaos Convocation and Officer Installation
DESCRIPTION:Rosicrucians AMORC\, Santa Rosa\, CA\n**Pronaos Convocation fo
 r Rosicrucian Members Only**\n**Installation of Officers**\n\n**Pronaos To
 pic - Education**\n**Presented by Frank Nappi\, F.R.C.**\nAll current memb
 ers of the Rosicrucian Order AMORC are cordially invited to participate in
  this first convocation of the Rosicrucian New Year. We will be installing
  new officers and celebrating the return of the Spring season and the star
 t of Rosicrucian year 3379.\n\n• Important to know- Doors open for membe
 rs of the Rosicrucian Order by 6:30 PM. Please arrive early! Members - ple
 ase bring your credentials or membership dues receipt.\n\nFollowing the me
 eting:\n1st Tuesday- Mystical Seekers Series Public Presentation at 8:00 P
 M\n\nThe Santa Rosa Pronaos operates under the law of AMRA. You may give a
 s your heart and mind direct you.\n\nThe Santa Rosa Pronaos is a 501c3 edu
 cational non-profit\, an affiliated body of the Rosicrucian English Grand 
 Lodge for the Americas and the Caribbean.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/amorc-santa-rosa-pronaos/events/31374
 4094/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260311T153628Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260311T153628Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
