SUMMARY:First Tuesday Mystical Seekers Series
DESCRIPTION:Rosicrucians AMORC\, Santa Rosa\, CA\n-Free Admission - Refres
 hments - Open to the public -\n\nTopic to be announced.....\nSpeaker to be
  announced......\n\nAbout the Santa Rosa Pronaos\nWe hold a monthly public
  presentation on mystical or metaphysical topics as a public service. The 
 topics and speakers vary and no previous knowledge or experience is requir
 ed. Just bring an open mind and heart.\n\nThe Santa Rosa Pronaos doesn't c
 harge for admission. We operate under the law of AMRA. You may give as you
 r heart and mind direct you.\n\nThe Santa Rosa Pronaos of the Rosicrucian 
 Order\, AMORC is a 501c3 Educational Nonprofit.
